OL,3,CWho will Iran's next supreme leader
OL,4,Cbe, as Trump says US 'must be involved'
OL,6,FSix days after the killing of Iran's
OL,7,FSupreme Leader Ali Khamenei, and under
OL,8,Fcontinued bombardment from the US and
OL,9,FIsrael, Iran is yet to confirm who its
OL,10,Fnext leader will be.
OL,12,FThe Trump administration has
OL,13,Frepeatedly asserted its desire to be
OL,14,Finvolved in choosing Iran's next
OL,15,Fleader, with the president calling for
OL,16,Fthe new leader to "bring harmony and
OL,17,Fpeace."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
