PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772917925
OL,3,CWho will Iran's next supreme leader
OL,4,Cbe, as Trump says US 'must be involved'
OL,6,FOn Thursday, US President Donald Trump
OL,7,Ftold Axios he wanted to be personally
OL,8,Finvolved in selecting Iran's next
OL,9,Fleader, comparing the situation to the
OL,10,FUS's recent actions in Venezuela,
OL,11,Fleading the UK's Deputy Prime Minister
OL,12,FDavid Lammy to label Trump's rhetoric
OL,13,Fas "intense".
OL,15,FSpeaking to Axios, Trump said: "They
OL,16,Fare wasting their time. Khamenei's son
OL,17,Fis a lightweight. I have to be
OL,18,Finvolved in the appointment, like with
OL,19,FDelcy (Rodriguez) in Venezuela."
OL,26,@{D@Gpm{D@Qpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
