CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772917925
OL,3,CWho will Iran's next supreme leader
OL,4,Cbe, as Trump says US 'must be involved'
OL,6,FIsrael's defence minister has also
OL,7,Falready labelled Khamenei's successor
OL,8,Fas a "target of elimination", should
OL,9,Fthey be deemed a threat.
OL,11,FAs outlined in its constitution, Iran
OL,12,Fon Sunday formed a council to assume
OL,13,Fleadership duties and govern the
OL,14,Fcountry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
