PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772917925
OL,3,CWho will Iran's next supreme leader
OL,4,Cbe, as Trump says US 'must be involved'
OL,6,FThe council is made up of Iran's
OL,7,Fsitting president, the head of the
OL,8,Fcountry's judiciary and a member of
OL,9,Fthe Guardian Council chosen by Iran's
OL,10,FExpediency Council, which advises the
OL,11,Fsupreme leader and settles disputes
OL,12,Fwith parliament.
OL,14,FThough the leadership council will
OL,15,Fgovern in the interim, an 88-member
OL,16,Fpanel called the Assembly of Experts
OL,17,Fmust "as soon as possible" pick a new
OL,18,Fsupreme leader under Iranian law.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
