OL,3,CWho will Iran's next supreme leader
OL,4,Cbe, as Trump says US 'must be involved'
OL,6,FThere has been only one other transfer
OL,7,Fof power in the office of supreme
OL,8,Fleader of Iran, the paramount decision-
OL,9,Fmaker since the country's 1979 Islamic
OL,10,FRevolution. This happened when the
OL,11,FGrand Ayatollah Ruhollah Khomeini died
OL,12,Fin 1989.
OL,14,FThe supreme leader is at the heart of
OL,15,FIran's complex power-sharing Shiite
OL,16,Ftheocracy and has final say over all
OL,17,Fmatters of state.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
