OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772917925
OL,3,CWho will Iran's next supreme leader
OL,4,Cbe, as Trump says US 'must be involved'
OL,6,FBut who is in the running to be the
OL,7,Fnext supreme leader, and what will
OL,8,Ftheir appointment mean for the Iranian
OL,9,Fregime going forward?
OL,11,FMojtaba Khamenei
OL,13,FThe son of Iran's recently killed
OL,14,FSupreme Leader Ali Khamenei, Mojtaba
OL,15,FKhamenei is seen by many as the
OL,16,Fpreferred candidate to replace his
OL,17,Ffather.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772917925
OL,3,CWho will Iran's next supreme leader
OL,4,Cbe, as Trump says US 'must be involved'
OL,6,FFor years, he has operated as a
OL,7,Fgatekeeper to his father, shaping
OL,8,Faccess, influence and decision-making
OL,9,Fwithin the inner circle of the Islamic
OL,10,FRepublic.
OL,12,FBut many in the US administration
OL,13,Fwould feel the younger Khamenei is the
OL,14,Fopposite of who they would want to
OL,15,Flead the Iranian regime.
OL,17,FUS President Donald Trump described
OL,18,Fhim on Thursday as an "unacceptable"
OL,19,Fcandidate, and a "lightweight".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772917925
OL,3,CWho will Iran's next supreme leader
OL,4,Cbe, as Trump says US 'must be involved'
OL,6,F"Khamenei's son is unacceptable to me.
OL,7,FWe want someone who will bring harmony
OL,8,Fand peace to Iran," he said, speaking
OL,9,Fto Axios.
OL,11,F"They are wasting their time.
OL,12,FKhamenei's son is a lightweight. I
OL,13,Fhave to be involved in the
OL,14,Fappointment, like with Delcy in
OL,15,FVenezuela," he said.
OL,17,FTrump also told Axios that he refused
OL,18,Fto accept someone who would continue
OL,19,Fthe existing policies of the existing
OL,20,FIranian regime.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
