OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772917925
OL,3,CWho will Iran's next supreme leader
OL,4,Cbe, as Trump says US 'must be involved'
OL,6,FIn 2009, he was reported to have taken
OL,7,Fcontrol of the militia being used to
OL,8,Fcrush a protest movement. He is also
OL,9,Fsaid to play a significant role in
OL,10,FIran's state broadcasting and
OL,11,Fpropaganda apparatus ` the same
OL,12,Fmachinery now tasked with framing his
OL,13,Ffather's death.
OL,15,FHis wife, Zahra Haddad Adel, who came
OL,16,Ffrom a family long associated with the
OL,17,Fcountry's theocracy, was killed in the
OL,18,Fsame strike that eliminated his father
OL,19,Fon Saturday.
OL,21,FAlireza Arafi
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
