OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772917925
OL,3,CWho will Iran's next supreme leader
OL,4,Cbe, as Trump says US 'must be involved'
OL,6,FDescribed by some as a hardline
OL,7,Fcleric, Arafi currently sits on the
OL,8,Finterim three-person council charged
OL,9,Fwith leading Iran until a new supreme
OL,10,Fleader is selected.
OL,12,FHe previously served as the head of Al-
OL,13,FMustafa International University, an
OL,14,Festablishment with a presence in more
OL,15,Fthan 50 countries designed to promote
OL,16,FIran's religious ideology abroad.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
