PN,31612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772917925
OL,3,CWho will Iran's next supreme leader
OL,4,Cbe, as Trump says US 'must be involved'
OL,6,FHe is a member of the Assembly of
OL,7,FExperts, and has been involved with
OL,8,Fthe selection and vetting of election
OL,9,Fcandidates through his work on the
OL,10,Fguardian council.
OL,12,FHis views are seen as closely allied
OL,13,Fwith those of the late Ali Khamenei,
OL,14,Fand his election is not thought to
OL,15,Fpose any serious deviation from Iran's
OL,16,Fpre-existing goals, with Arafi being
OL,17,Fthought of as fundamentally aligned
OL,18,Fwith the religious leadership that has
OL,19,Fgoverned Iran for decades.
OL,21,FHassan Khomeini
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
