PN,31613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772917925
OL,3,CWho will Iran's next supreme leader
OL,4,Cbe, as Trump says US 'must be involved'
OL,6,FThe grandson of the Islamic
OL,7,FRevolution's founding father,
OL,8,FAyatollah Ruhollah Khomeini, Hassan
OL,9,FKhomeini is thought of as a more
OL,10,Fmoderate contender to replace Ali
OL,11,FKhamenei.
OL,13,FWith ties to former Iranian presidents
OL,14,Fwho shared a history of engagement
OL,15,Fwith the West when in office, his
OL,16,Fdeparture from the more hardline
OL,17,Fpolicies of his predecessor could be
OL,18,Fseen as a positive in the White House.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
