PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772917925
OL,3,CWho will Iran's next supreme leader
OL,4,Cbe, as Trump says US 'must be involved'
OL,6,FAccording to Iran International, while
OL,7,Fspeaking at his grandfather's
OL,8,Fmausoleum in May last year, Khomeini
OL,9,Fremarked that dignity can arise either
OL,10,Ffrom war or from steadfastness in
OL,11,Fnegotiation.
OL,13,FHis views saw him previously
OL,14,Fdisqualified from the 2016 assembly of
OL,15,Fexperts election.
OL,17,FHe has four children with his wife
OL,18,FSayyeda Fatima, the daughter of an
OL,19,Fayatollah.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
