OL,3,CWho will Iran's next supreme leader
OL,4,Cbe, as Trump says US 'must be involved'
OL,6,FHe has been vocal in his criticisms
OL,7,Fbefore, calling for accountability in
OL,8,Fthe wake of the killing of Kurdish-
OL,9,FIranian Masha Amini.
OL,11,FSpeaking at the time, he said
OL,12,Fauthorities "must transparently and
OL,13,Fprecisely account for what has
OL,14,Fhappened to this 22-year-old girl
OL,15,Funder the pretext of 'guidance and
OL,16,Feducation'".
OL,18,FMasha Amini died in custody after
OL,19,Fbeing arrested by Iran's strict
OL,20,Fmorality police for an alleged breach
OL,21,Fof the country's dress code for women.
OL,26,@tD@MOUxD@KO]
