OL,3,CWho will Iran's next supreme leader
OL,4,Cbe, as Trump says US 'must be involved'
OL,6,FFollowing the killing of Supreme
OL,7,FLeader Ali Khamenei, he wrote in a
OL,8,Fletter that the late leader would "be
OL,9,Fthe hero of the people of Iran and
OL,10,FMuslims.
OL,12,F"The noble people of Iran will once
OL,13,Fagain walk the path of the Imam
OL,14,F(Khomeini) by overcoming this
OL,15,Fincident."
OL,17,FOther candidates?
