OL,3,CWho will Iran's next supreme leader
OL,4,Cbe, as Trump says US 'must be involved'
OL,6,FAcross multiple press conferences, the
OL,7,FUS has appeared to change its
OL,8,Fmotivations and aims for the current
OL,9,Fconflict in Iran.
OL,11,FThe at times mercurial nature of
OL,12,FTrump's foreign policy makes it
OL,13,Fdifficult to predict exactly who the
OL,14,FUS administration would favour as a
OL,15,Fleader in Iran.
OL,17,FAdded to this is the fact many who the
OL,18,FUS assumed would be front runners in
OL,19,Fthe line of sucession appear to have
OL,20,Falso been eliminated in the strike
OL,21,Fthat killed Khamenei.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
