SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772917925
OL,3,CWho will Iran's next supreme leader
OL,4,Cbe, as Trump says US 'must be involved'
OL,6,FThe US has denied regime change is the
OL,7,Fultimate aim of their military
OL,8,Foperations, but on Tuesday, when asked
OL,9,Fabout succession, Trump told
OL,10,Freporters: "Most of the people we had
OL,11,Fin mind are dead."
OL,13,FAlthough not a candidate being
OL,14,Fconsidered by the assembly of experts,
OL,15,Fthe son of the last Shah of Iran, Reza
OL,16,FPahlavi, has recently been a rallying
OL,17,Ffigure behind protests in the country,
OL,18,Fseeking to rally Iranian people behind
OL,19,Fhim in overthrowing the regime.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
