SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772917925
OL,3,CWho will Iran's next supreme leader
OL,4,Cbe, as Trump says US 'must be involved'
OL,6,FCurrently living in exile, Trump has
OL,7,Fpreviously said he believes someone
OL,8,Falready in Iran would be best placed
OL,9,Fto take over, adding: "I don't know
OL,10,Fwhether or not his country would
OL,11,Faccept his leadership.
OL,13,F"Certainly if they would, that would
OL,14,Fbe fine with me."
OL,16,FPahlavi has claimed he is "uniquely
OL,17,Fplaced" to lead a transitional
OL,18,Fgovernment, indicating he would be
OL,19,Fwilling to return to Iran to do so.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
